::  Causeway management mark — opaque sotx passthrough. gall needs a mark
::  file to type-cast pokes; this one is trivial since our agent handler
::  just extracts the vase.
/-  urb
|_  =sotx:urb
++  grad  %noun
++  grow  |%  ++  noun  sotx  --
++  grab  |%  ++  noun  sotx:urb  --
++  grit  |%  ++  noun  sotx  --
--
